                        <seg type="rubrication">Holy names; groups of lines alternating with black
                           lines in the incipit page of Text I-1; headings and incipits of the
                           texts, their sections and subsections; titles of the Biblical books and
                           other works; names of Hebrew letters in Text I-8; directives for the
                           ministers; abbreviations in Texts I-8 and I-9; some words, e.g.: yǝbe,
                           yǝtärägʷǝm in Text I-8; elements of the punctuation signs and of the
                           Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
